  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This will be the most thrilling pool game you have ever played. Join up to 3 of your friends in this exciting pool roulette game! Eliminate each other with pool until only one person is left. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/71f0549f497c9ae62e70998d4606bda4.webp?t=1770639491\" width=710 height=4 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The most exciting pool game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Either clear the table with one shot, or pick up the revolver and listen to your heartbeat...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/515a21cdf081fa4a354366803f3c51a0.poster.avif?t=1770639491\" width=460 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/515a21cdf081fa4a354366803f3c51a0.webm?t=1770639491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/515a21cdf081fa4a354366803f3c51a0.mp4?t=1770639491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/71f0549f497c9ae62e70998d4606bda4.webp?t=1770639491\" width=710 height=4 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Show off your pool skills! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you the king of powerful shots or the king of trick shots? I personally prefer high left spin with a bit of low right spin. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/4aa61f8ea6a3c6e86fc78962028591bb.poster.avif?t=1770639491\" width=460 height=214 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/4aa61f8ea6a3c6e86fc78962028591bb.webm?t=1770639491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/4aa61f8ea6a3c6e86fc78962028591bb.mp4?t=1770639491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/71f0549f497c9ae62e70998d4606bda4.webp?t=1770639491\" width=710 height=4 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rich interaction, unlimited joy in voice chat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Exciting interactions, never fear being without billiards friends again! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/6ef114d4b162de22d7fe3a31085f3f71.poster.avif?t=1770639491\" width=460 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/6ef114d4b162de22d7fe3a31085f3f71.webm?t=1770639491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/6ef114d4b162de22d7fe3a31085f3f71.mp4?t=1770639491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This will be the most thrilling pool game you have ever played. Join up to 3 of your friends in this exciting pool roulette game! Eliminate each other with pool until only one person is left. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/71f0549f497c9ae62e70998d4606bda4.webp?t=1770639491\" width=710 height=4 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The most exciting pool game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Either clear the table with one shot, or pick up the revolver and listen to your heartbeat...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/515a21cdf081fa4a354366803f3c51a0.poster.avif?t=1770639491\" width=460 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/515a21cdf081fa4a354366803f3c51a0.webm?t=1770639491\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/515a21cdf081fa4a354366803f3c51a0.mp4?t=1770639491\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/71f0549f497c9ae62e70998d4606bda4.webp?t=1770639491\" width=710 height=4 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Show off your pool skills! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you the king of powerful shots or the king of trick shots? I personally prefer high left spin with a bit of low right spin. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3376250/extras/4aa61f8ea6a3c6e8